## ğŸ“ File Descriptions

### ğŸ“Œ Constants

#### **app_constants.dart**
- App information and versioning
- Network timeouts and pagination
- User roles and statuses
- Order and payment status constants
- Transaction types
- Validation constraints
- Error and success messages
- Feature flags
- Business rules (minimum order, delivery fees, etc.)

#### **firebase_constants.dart**
- Firestore collection names
- Firebase Storage paths
- Field names for all collections
- Query limits and operators
- Firebase error codes
- FCM topics and notification types
- Compound query index names

#### **route_constants.dart**
- All app route paths
- Route names for navigation
- Helper methods for generating routes with IDs
- Deep link paths
- Route guards for role-based access
- Query parameters

---

### ğŸ¨ Theme

#### **colors.dart**
- Brand colors (primary, secondary, accent)
- Semantic colors (success, error, warning, info)
- Neutral colors (white, black, grays)
- Text colors for light/dark themes
- Background and surface colors
- Status colors (order, payment, production, stock)
- Role colors
- Chart colors
- Gradient definitions
- Helper methods for color manipulation

#### **text_styles.dart**
- Complete typography system following Material 3
- Display, headline, title, body, and label styles
- Button and input text styles
- Custom app-specific styles (price, badge, stats, etc.)
- Message styles (error, success, warning, info)
- Helper methods for text style modifications

#### **app_theme.dart**
- Complete light theme configuration
- Complete dark theme configuration
- Color schemes for both themes
- Component themes (AppBar, Card, Button, etc.)
- Input decoration theme
- All Material widgets themed consistently

