- Price and quantity validation
- Date validation (current, future, past)
- Address validation
- URL validation
- Credit card validation (with Luhn algorithm)
- CVV and expiry date validation
- Helper methods and validator combiners

#### **formatters.dart**
- Phone number formatters
- Currency formatters
- Credit card formatters
- Numeric formatters (digits, decimal, percentage)
- Text formatters (uppercase, lowercase, capitalize)
- Length limiters
- Weight and measurement formatters
- Duration formatters
- File size formatters
- Rating formatters
- Custom pattern formatters
- Truncation methods

#### **date_utils.dart**
- Date formatting (display, API, custom patterns)
- Date parsing
- Relative time ("2 hours ago", "in 3 days")
- Date comparison (today, yesterday, this week, etc.)
- Date manipulation (start/end of day, week, month, year)
- Date range utilities
- Business date calculations
- Age calculation
- Duration calculations
- Month and day name getters
- Friendly date displays

#### **currency_utils.dart**
- Currency formatting (with/without symbol, separators)
- Currency parsing
- Financial calculations (tax, discount, subtotal, total)
- Delivery fee calculations
- Rounding methods
- Amount comparison
- Validation methods
- Conversion methods (cents â†” dollars)
- Amount distribution and splitting
- Aggregation methods (sum, average, min, max)
- Percentage calculations
